1
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,500
Here's a list of colors and materials.
这是一张颜色和材料的清单.

2
00:00:09,700 --> 00:00:11,100
If you ever want to match something,
如果你要配点什么,

3
00:00:11,170 --> 00:00:12,050
take the list to the store.
可以带这张单子去店里买.

4
00:00:12,170 --> 00:00:13,400
Thanks.
谢谢.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,708
And here's your final invoice.
这是你最后的发票.

6
00:00:15,736 --> 00:00:19,900
Fine. I can write a check now, if that's OK.
好的.我现在就可以开支票,如果没问题的话.

7
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:23,400
Bill, you're my favorite client.
Bill,你是我最喜欢的顾客.

8
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:26,000
I just wish I had more than two rooms for you to do.
我真希望我有超过两个房间可以请你们装潢.

9
00:00:26,154 --> 00:00:28,900
Just call us when you have a house, OK?
等你有了大房子就给我们打电话,好吗?

10
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,500
I'm sure all your clients come back.
我相信你们所有的客户都会成为回头客.

11
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:34,100
All but one.
只有一个不是.

12
00:00:34,900 --> 00:00:39,000
Oh, really? You have to tell me.
Oh,真的?这你得跟我讲讲.

13
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:40,600
I'm your favorite client.
我可是你们最喜欢的顾客.

14
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:43,700
He had no sense of color.
他对色彩没有一点感觉.

15
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:50,700
One day last summer, we got a call.
去年夏季的一天,我们接到个电话.

16
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:56,550
It was a doctor, a very successful surgeon
是一位医生,一位非常成功的外科医生

17
00:00:56,616 --> 00:01:00,000
who wanted us to design his consulting offices.
他想请我们设计他的诊室.

18
00:01:00,104 --> 00:01:02,800
And it was very important to the big surgeon...
对那位名医来说,有一点非常重要

19
00:01:02,989 --> 00:01:04,000
Nan...
Nan...

20
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:06,600
...that the colors be soothing.
色彩要让人感到平和、放松.

21
00:01:06,806 --> 00:01:08,700
Well, that makes sense.
Well,有道理.

22
00:01:08,841 --> 00:01:10,700
I had no problem with that.
对此我毫无异议.

23
00:01:10,814 --> 00:01:19,200
However, the surgeon and my partner could not agree on green.
但是,那位外科医生与我的合伙人在绿色的问题上意见不一致.

24
00:01:19,340 --> 00:01:22,800
Green is...green, right?
绿色就是绿色，对不对?

25
00:01:22,937 --> 00:01:26,400
It was a very soft sea foam green, 
是种非常柔和的海水泡沫般的绿色,

26
00:01:26,511 --> 00:01:28,950
very gentle on the eyes.
有非常柔和的视觉效果.

27
00:01:29,033 --> 00:01:30,400
What color is that?
那是什么颜色?

28
00:01:30,565 --> 00:01:31,600
Green.
绿色.

29
00:01:31,721 --> 00:01:32,800
Thank you.
谢谢.

30
00:01:32,917 --> 00:01:38,500
Well, the surgeon said the green was yellowy-brown 
Well,那位外科医生把那种绿色说成是黄褐色,

31
00:01:38,645 --> 00:01:40,500
and not relaxing at all.
而且根本无法让人放松.

32
00:01:40,677 --> 00:01:44,500
In fact, he said the green was...
事实上,他说那种绿色是...

33
00:01:45,060 --> 00:01:45,911
what did he call it?
他怎么说来着?

34
00:01:46,076 --> 00:01:49,900
Institutional. Do you believe it? 
单调俗套的.你相信吗?

35
00:01:50,097 --> 00:01:52,600
He gave me such a headache.
他让我如此头痛.

36
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:57,400
Green, yellow, green, yellow. 
绿色,黄色,绿色,黄色.

37
00:01:57,700 --> 00:02:01,135
We finally went with a shade of pink...
最后我们用了一种粉色...

38
00:02:01,276 --> 00:02:02,700
Which he called violet.
他说那是紫色.

39
00:02:02,830 --> 00:02:05,900
And the man is an eye surgeon!
这人居然是个眼外科医生!

